課程概述 Course Description
       探討神經生理學之最新進展及原理，使研究生對於神經生理學有深入完整的瞭解及認識。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    修習本課程之研究生對於神經生理學有深入完整的瞭解及認識。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introductionto Neurophysiology 2Nerve cells and Behavior3Cell and Molecular Biology of the Neuron (I)4Cell and Molecular Biology of the Neuron (II)5Synaptic Transmission (I) 6Synaptic Transmission (II)7Synaptic Transmission (III) 8The Neural Basis of Cognition 9Perception (I) 10Perception (II) 11The Development of Nervous System (I)12The Development of Nervous System (II)13The Development of Nervous System (III)14Learning and Memory (I) 15Learning and Memory (II) 16Learning and Memory (III) 17Student Presentations (I)18Student Presentations (II) 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


